msg_8:
The man held up both hands. While keeping him   
in my peripheral vision, I maintained my stance    
and smoothly moved around him towards the elevator, 
all the while my blade remained against his forehead. 
[wait][clear][end]

msg_9:
He groped one-handed for the elevator button, 
and after a moment, the door opened.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_10:
My blade still against him, I walked in
without hesitation, while he bent back
and revolved into the cage back-first.
[sync][wait][clear][end]

msg_11:
I kicked him in the chin. Momentarily knocking him 
senseless, I grabbed the nape of his neck, made him 
stand up, shoved his face into the button panel and 
stole the automatic handgun off his hip.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_12:
When I released the safety and pulled back the slide, 
I found that one of the bullets had already been fired. 
I ejected the shell and let it roll towards the floor.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_13:
I was just aping Maya-nee, I should’ve 
been able to handle this weapon alright. 
I pressed the muzzle up to the back of the man’s ear.
[sync][wait][clear][end]

