[sync][wait][clear][end]

msg_15:
With blood dripping from his forehead and nose, 
the man pushed the buttons 31123213B1 in that order. 
When he pushed the G button slightly downwards, 
the elevator began to move.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_16:
I grabbed the nape of his neck and made the man 
stand in front of the doors. If this was a trap, 
he’d be the one getting shot for it.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_17:
When we passed the third floor, the number 3 on the 
panel’s floor number indicator started flickering. 
Several seconds passed, and the doors opened. 
It looked like we had reached the fourth floor.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_18:
I’d figured security guards would be lying in wait, 
but no one was here. 
I pushed the man forward and left the elevator.
[sync][wait][clear][end]
